    "comment_data": [
        {
            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "These tests fail, in the code paths, according to twopossibiltieis:\n\n1. curl failed and the helper returned `{ error = \"...\" }`\n2. curl succeeded, but httpbingo.org/anything returned JSON without a method field.\n\nI'm not some clean code obsessor here but having network dependencies in a test suite... no.\n\n## appropriate changes\n\n1.  the tests use `eq()` with expected, actual in opposite order\n2. either a) mock the entire suite (no) or b) set up a proxy/shim server to receive requests (decent)\n\nthoughts on this @ellisonleao - want to leave the changes to you but open to work on it w/ ur permission.",
